<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4402822>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 128–134. Male morphology of Winnertzia pustulatula (128–131) and Winnertzia ruliki (132–134), holotypes. 128: Genitalia, ventral. 129: Gonostylus, ventral. 130: Fourth flagellomere, lateral. 131: Ditto, medial. 132: Genitalia, ventral. 133: Fourth flagellomere, lateral. 134: Ditto, medial. Scales for 128 and 130–134, 0.05 mm; for 129, 0.025 mm. Arrows refer to characters described in the diagnoses." ;
